issue.title: Parser needs to be tested
issue.body:
Sometimes certain functions are not found - this needs to be fixed. 

Currently there are no unit-tests, which is bad. We need to test each scoping-rule to find the bugs and detect future regressions.

Example of errors:
- Method: `set` Type: `java.util.ArrayList`
- Method: `open` Type: `java.io.InputStream`
- Method: `getPlugin` Type: `org.intellimate.izou.addon.AddOnModel`

It seems like only very popular functions are found
